(24, 1, 'Канцелярия для школы', '&lt;p class=&quot;description-robotolight&quot;&gt;Накануне наступления школьной поры начинается период активного наполнения портфелей. Один из пунктов списка покупок к учебному году — канцелярия, которая пригодится красноярскому школьнику в течение последующих девяти месяцев.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n &lt;h1 class=&quot;title-article&quot;&gt;Канцелярия первой необходимости&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n &lt;p class=&quot;description-robotolight&quot;&gt;Начинать покупку снаряжения лучше всего с самого необходимого — с шариковых ручек, которые, если верить красноярским статистикам, в этом году заметно прибавили в цене. Как выбрать хорошую ручку? Во-первых, верная спутница школьника должна удобно лежать в руке: кисть не будет уставать, а навыки письма будут развиваться быстрее. Так что о толстом корпусе лучше забыть. Меньше внимания красивым картинкам — больше внимания к практической стороне вопроса. Во-вторых, толщина линии должна быть средней. С ручкой, которая пишет «жирно», ваш ребенок может не справиться — письмо не будет аккуратным. &lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;\r\n\r\nСлишком тонкие стержни тоже лучше оставить для людей постарше, с ними гораздо сложнее справляться. Оптимальная толщина стержня — 1.00 мм. Наконец, в-третьих, ручка не должна течь и пачкать руки — в противном случае вы рискуете расстаться со школьной формой, перепачканной чернилами, а ребенок — заработать репутацию грязнули. Обязательно проверьте, как пишет ручка — и в магазине, и дома. Отдавайте предпочтение проверенным брендам: BIC, Cello, Proff, Wateman, Stabilo и т. д. Вам подойдут шариковые ручки и на масляных чернилах (стоят дороже и тратят больше чернил). Одна шариковая ручка обойдется в 15-50 рублей. Если вы нашли идеальный вариант — смело берите с десяток.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n &lt;div class=&quot;img-article&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;img src=&quot;/catalog/view/theme/itstep-theme/bp-site-1/img/img-article4.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n &lt;h1 class=&quot;title-article&quot;&gt;Канцелярия для творчества\r\n		&lt;/h1&gt;\r\n  &lt;p class=&quot;description-robotolight&quot;&gt;\r\n			По поводу «творческой» канцелярии лучше всего навести справки у классного руководителя и учителей. Скорее всего, сюда войдут цветные карандаши, фломастеры, пластилин, альбом для рисования и краски, но список может меняться в зависимости от программы занятий. Поговорим о базовых предметах для творчества. &lt;br&gt; &lt;br&gt;\r\n\r\nЦветные карандаши выбираем по тем же правилам, что и простые карандаши. Но обращать внимание нужно на большее количество вещей. Помимо жесткости и характеристик корпуса и грифеля, обратите внимание на насыщенность оттенков, их разнообразие. Также выбирать придется между восковыми, акварельными, пластиковыми и деревянными цветными карандашами. 12 цветов будет достаточно. Цена вопроса — от 50 до 200 рублей, в зависимости от марки и качества.\r\n		&lt;/p&gt;\r\n &lt;div class=&quot;img-article&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;img src=&quot;/catalog/view/theme/itstep-theme/bp-site-1/img/img-article5.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n &lt;div class=&quot;article-leftright clearfix&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;article-left&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;source&quot;&gt;Источник - &lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;\r\n	http://oskanov.livejournal.com/475636.html \r\n&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;tags-article2&quot;&gt;#\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;tags-article1&quot;&gt;дети&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;tags-article2&quot;&gt;#\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;tags-article1&quot;&gt;обучение&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;tags-article2&quot;&gt;#\r\n&lt;span class=&quot;tags-article1&quot;&gt;канцелярия&lt;/span&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;article-right&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;div class=&quot;repost-article&quot;&gt;\r\n\r\n	&lt;span&gt;Поделиться статьей в социальной сети&lt;/span&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/catalog/view/theme/itstep-theme/bp-site-1/img/repost-article/vk.png&quot; alt=&quot;vk&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/catalog/view/theme/itstep-theme/bp-site-1/img/repost-article/google.png&quot; alt=&quot;google&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/catalog/view/theme/itstep-theme/bp-site-1/img/repost-article/facebook.png&quot; alt=&quot;facebook&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/catalog/view/theme/itstep-theme/bp-site-1/img/repost-article/od.png&quot; alt=&quot;OD&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/catalog/view/theme/itstep-theme/bp-site-1/img/repost-article/twitter.png&quot; alt=&quot;twitter&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n		&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/catalog/view/theme/itstep-theme/bp-site-1/img/repost-article/insta.png&quot; alt=&quot;instagram&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;div id=&quot;comment_bubble&quot;&gt;55&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/div&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;/div&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(112, 112, 112); font-family: Roboto-Light; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;Накануне наступления школьной поры начинается период активного наполнения портфелей. Один из пунктов списка покупок к учебному году — канцелярия, которая пригодится красноярскому школьнику в течение последующих девяти месяцев.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'Although we now have smartphones with displays that measure more than 6 inches, most tablets are still just tablets. Even if they feature 3G or LTE connectivity, they don’t offer phone capabilities. However', 'tablet,tab,phone', 'дети,обучение,канцелярия'),
(20, 1, 'Computer keyboard', '&lt;p&gt;In &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computing&quot; title=&quot;Computing&quot;&gt;computing&lt;/a&gt;, a &lt;b&gt;keyboard&lt;/b&gt; is a &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Typewriter#Keyboard_layouts:_.22QWERTY.22_and_others&quot; title=&quot;Typewriter&quot;&gt;typewriter-style device&lt;/a&gt;, which uses an arrangement of buttons or &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Push-button&quot; title=&quot;Push-button&quot;&gt;keys&lt;/a&gt;, to act as mechanical levers or electronic switches. Following the decline of &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Punch_card&quot; title=&quot;Punch card&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot;&gt;punch cards&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paper_tape&quot; title=&quot;Paper tape&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot;&gt;paper tape&lt;/a&gt;, interaction via &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Teleprinter&quot; title=&quot;Teleprinter&quot;&gt;teleprinter&lt;/a&gt;-style keyboards became the main &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Input_device&quot; title=&quot;Input device&quot;&gt;input device&lt;/a&gt; for &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer&quot; title=&quot;Computer&quot;&gt;computers&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;A keyboard typically has characters &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Engraving&quot; title=&quot;Engraving&quot;&gt;engraved&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Printing&quot; title=&quot;Printing&quot;&gt;printed&lt;/a&gt; on the keys and each press of a key typically corresponds to a single written &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Symbol&quot; title=&quot;Symbol&quot;&gt;symbol&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n However, to produce some symbols requires pressing and holding several \r\nkeys simultaneously or in sequence. While most keyboard keys produce &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Letter_%28alphabet%29&quot; title=&quot;Letter (alphabet)&quot;&gt;letters&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Numerical_digit&quot; title=&quot;Numerical digit&quot;&gt;numbers&lt;/a&gt; or signs (&lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Character_%28computing%29&quot; title=&quot;Character (computing)&quot;&gt;characters&lt;/a&gt;), other keys or simultaneous key presses can produce actions or execute computer commands.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Despite the development of alternative input devices, such as the &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mouse_%28computing%29&quot; title=&quot;Mouse (computing)&quot;&gt;mouse&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Touchscreen&quot; title=&quot;Touchscreen&quot;&gt;touchscreen&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pen_computing&quot; title=&quot;Pen computing&quot;&gt;pen devices&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Character_recognition&quot; title=&quot;Character recognition&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot;&gt;character recognition&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Speech_recognition&quot; title=&quot;Speech recognition&quot;&gt;voice recognition&lt;/a&gt;, the keyboard remains the most commonly used device for direct (human) input of &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alphanumeric&quot; title=&quot;Alphanumeric&quot;&gt;alphanumeric&lt;/a&gt; data into computers.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;In normal usage, the keyboard is used as a &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Text_Entry_Interface&quot; title=&quot;Text Entry Interface&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot;&gt;text entry interface&lt;/a&gt; to type text and numbers into a &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Word_processor&quot; title=&quot;Word processor&quot;&gt;word processor&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Text_editor&quot; title=&quot;Text editor&quot;&gt;text editor&lt;/a&gt;\r\n or other programs. In a modern computer, the interpretation of key \r\npresses is generally left to the software. A computer keyboard \r\ndistinguishes each physical key from every other and reports all key \r\npresses to the controlling software. Keyboards are also used for \r\ncomputer gaming, either with regular keyboards or by using keyboards \r\nwith special gaming features, which can expedite frequently used \r\nkeystroke combinations. A keyboard is also used to give commands to the \r\noperating system of a computer, such as &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Microsoft_Windows&quot; title=&quot;Microsoft Windows&quot;&gt;Windows&lt;/a&gt;'' &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Control-Alt-Delete&quot; title=&quot;Control-Alt-Delete&quot;&gt;Control-Alt-Delete&lt;/a&gt; combination, which brings up a task window or shuts down the machine. A &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Command-line_interface&quot; title=&quot;Command-line interface&quot;&gt;command-line interface&lt;/a&gt; is a type of &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/User_interface&quot; title=&quot;User interface&quot;&gt;user interface&lt;/a&gt; operated entirely through a keyboard, or another device doing the job of one.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mw-headline&quot; id=&quot;History&quot;&gt;History&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;While typewriters are the definitive ancestor of all key-based text \r\nentry devices, the computer keyboard as a device for electromechanical \r\ndata entry and communication derives largely from the utility of two \r\ndevices: teleprinters (or teletypes) and &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keypunch&quot; title=&quot;Keypunch&quot;&gt;keypunches&lt;/a&gt;. It was through such devices that modern computer keyboards inherited their layouts.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;As early as the 1870s, teleprinter-like devices were used to simultaneously type and transmit &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stock_market&quot; title=&quot;Stock market&quot;&gt;stock market&lt;/a&gt; text data from the keyboard across telegraph lines to &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stock_ticker_machine&quot; title=&quot;Stock ticker machine&quot; class=&quot;mw-redirect&quot;&gt;stock ticker machines&lt;/a&gt; to be immediately copied and displayed onto &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ticker_tape&quot; title=&quot;Ticker tape&quot;&gt;ticker tape&lt;/a&gt;. The teleprinter, in its more contemporary form, was developed from 1907 to 1910 by American mechanical engineer &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Krum&quot; title=&quot;Charles Krum&quot;&gt;Charles Krum&lt;/a&gt; and his son &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Howard_Krum&amp;amp;action=edit&amp;amp;redlink=1&quot; class=&quot;new&quot; title=&quot;Howard Krum (page does not exist)&quot;&gt;Howard&lt;/a&gt;, with early contributions by electrical engineer &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Frank_Pearne&amp;amp;action=edit&amp;amp;redlink=1&quot; class=&quot;new&quot; title=&quot;Frank Pearne (page does not exist)&quot;&gt;Frank Pearne&lt;/a&gt;. Earlier models were developed separately by individuals such as &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Royal_Earl_House&quot; title=&quot;Royal Earl House&quot;&gt;Royal Earl House&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Frederick_G._Creed&quot; title=&quot;Frederick G. Creed&quot;&gt;Frederick G. Creed&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Earlier, &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Herman_Hollerith&quot; title=&quot;Herman Hollerith&quot;&gt;Herman Hollerith&lt;/a&gt;\r\n developed the first keypunch devices, which soon evolved to include \r\nkeys for text and number entry akin to normal typewriters by the 1930s.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The keyboard on the teleprinter played a strong role in \r\npoint-to-point and point-to-multipoint communication for most of the \r\n20th century, while the keyboard on the keypunch device played a strong \r\nrole in data entry and storage for just as long. The development of the \r\nearliest computers incorporated electric typewriter keyboards: the \r\ndevelopment of the &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ENIAC&quot; title=&quot;ENIAC&quot;&gt;ENIAC&lt;/a&gt; computer incorporated a keypunch device as both the input and paper-based output device, while the &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BINAC&quot; title=&quot;BINAC&quot;&gt;BINAC&lt;/a&gt;\r\n computer also made use of an electromechanically controlled typewriter \r\nfor both data entry onto magnetic tape (instead of paper) and data \r\noutput.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;From the 1940s until the late 1960s, typewriters were the main means \r\nof data entry and output for computing, becoming integrated into what \r\nwere known as &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Computer_terminal&quot; title=&quot;Computer terminal&quot;&gt;computer terminals&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n Because of the limitations of terminals based upon printed text in \r\ncomparison to the growth in data storage, processing and transmission, a\r\n general move toward video-based computer terminals was affected by the \r\n1970s, starting with the &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Datapoint_3300&quot; title=&quot;Datapoint 3300&quot;&gt;Datapoint 3300&lt;/a&gt; in 1967.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;The keyboard remained the primary, most integrated computer \r\nperipheral well into the era of personal computing until the \r\nintroduction of the mouse as a consumer device in 1984. By this time, \r\ntext-only user interfaces with sparse graphics gave way to &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Graphical_user_interface&quot; title=&quot;Graphical user interface&quot;&gt;comparatively graphics-rich icons on screen&lt;/a&gt;.\r\n However, keyboards remain central to human-computer interaction to the \r\npresent, even as mobile personal computing devices such as &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Smartphone&quot; title=&quot;Smartphone&quot;&gt;smartphones&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tablet_computer&quot; title=&quot;Tablet computer&quot;&gt;tablets&lt;/a&gt; adapt the keyboard as an optional virtual, touchscreen-based means of data entry.&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', '', 'keyboard'),
(20, 2, 'কম্পিউটার কীবোর্ড', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;একই ভাবে বেশ\r\nকিছুদিন আগেই&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:\r\nVrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;আমাদের\r\nব্যবসায়-বাণিজ্যে যুক্ত হয়েছে এই আধুনিক মাধ্যমটি। ফলে দিন দিন&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;বাড়ছে ই-বাণিজ্যের\r\nপ্রসার। বিভিন্ন সীমাবদ্ধতা স্বত্বেও বাংলাদেশে ইতিমধ্যে&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;কিছু ই-বাণিজ্য ওয়েবসাইট গড়ে উঠেছে।\r\nই-বাণিজ্যকে কাজে লাগিয়ে বাংলাদেশ&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;একদিকে যেমন ব্যবসা-বাণিজ্যের প্রভূত\r\nউন্নতি করা সম্ভব তেমনি একই সাথে&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;কর্মসংস্থানের ক্ষেত্রেও যুক্ত হয়েছে\r\nঅমিত সম্ভাবনা আর সমৃদ্ধির সুযোগ।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;তবে বিষয়টি সম্পর্কে পরিস্কার ধারণা নেই\r\nআমাদের অনেকেরই। সাধারণ মানুষদের&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;মধ্য ই-কমার্স সম্পর্কে সচেতনতা বৃদ্ধির\r\nলক্ষ্যে বাংলাদেশের জনপ্রিয় আইসিটি&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;ম্যাগাজিন কমপিউটার জগৎ ই-বাণিজ্য মেলা\r\n২০১৩ এর আয়োজন করতে যাচ্ছে&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;৭-৯ফেব্রুয়ারী)।\r\nএই মেলাতে দেশের বিভিন্ন ই-বাণিজ্য প্রতিষ্ঠান তাদের পণ্য&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;ও সেবা সমূহ সাধারণ মানুষের সামনে তুলে\r\nধরবে। মেলা অনুষ্ঠিত হবে ঢাকার&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;শাহবাগে অবস্থিত সুফিয়া কামাল জাতীয় গ্রন্থাগারে।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;সামহোয়‍্যার&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;ইন...ব্লগের পাঠকদের জন্যে ই-কমার্সের\r\nবিভিন্ন বিষয় শেয়ার করতে কমপিউটার&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;জগতের পক্ষ থেকে এই লেখাটির অবতারণা।\r\nআশা করি লেখাটি আমাদের অনেকেরেই কাজে&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;লাগবে।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;br&gt;\r\n&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;তবে বিষয়টি সম্পর্কে পরিস্কার ধারণা নেই\r\nআমাদের অনেকেরই। সাধারণ মানুষদের&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;মধ্য ই-কমার্স সম্পর্কে সচেতনতা বৃদ্ধির\r\nলক্ষ্যে বাংলাদেশের জনপ্রিয় আইসিটি&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;ম্যাগাজিন কমপিউটার জগৎ ই-বাণিজ্য মেলা\r\n২০১৩ এর আয়োজন করতে যাচ্ছে&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;\r\nmso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;৭-৯ফেব্রুয়ারী)।\r\nএই মেলাতে দেশের বিভিন্ন ই-বাণিজ্য প্রতিষ্ঠান তাদের পণ্য&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;ও সেবা সমূহ সাধারণ মানুষের সামনে তুলে\r\nধরবে। মেলা অনুষ্ঠিত হবে ঢাকার&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;mso-hansi-font-family:\r\n&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;শাহবাগে অবস্থিত সুফিয়া কামাল জাতীয় গ্রন্থাগারে।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;সামহোয়‍্যার&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;ইন...ব্লগের পাঠকদের জন্যে ই-কমার্সের\r\nবিভিন্ন বিষয় শেয়ার করতে কমপিউটার&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;জগতের পক্ষ থেকে এই লেখাটির অবতারণা।\r\nআশা করি লেখাটি আমাদের অনেকেরেই কাজে&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family:Vrinda;mso-ascii-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;;\r\nmso-hansi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times New Roman&amp;quot;&quot; lang=&quot;AR-SA&quot;&gt;লাগবে।&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'কীবোর্ড